Name: AttributeFix-Forge-1.19.2-17.2.8.jar
Description: Minecraft uses an attribute system to handle important calculations. It covers everything from armor values, to attack damage, to the maximum health of a mob. This system also introduced attribute caps, which limit how high any value can be. While this usually goes unnoticed, many mods are unknowingly affected by it. This mod significantly increases these caps to allow those mods to work as they were intended.
